Two options discussed

Option 1 — Preferred

API download approach
	•	Mukund’s team calls your API from their process
	•	API generates/returns the CSV
	•	File gets downloaded locally on their side
	•	They process it from there
	•	No need for NAS/shared path/job copying flow
